  <description><![CDATA[<p>With a reputation for high standards the Hotel Sonnenburg in Oberlech has proven itself to be a welcome addition to our winter programme. The Hoch family take great pride in offering their guests exceptional cuisine, first rate service and wonderful facilities.</p>
<p>Located above Lech and perfectly positioned next to the slopes the Sonnenburg is an ideal ski-in/out hotel. Lech itself is accessible by cable-car until 1am daily.</p>]]></description>
